      "title": "E231｜从B2B到A2A：Agent新基建，如何让“一人企业”做全球生意？",
      "url": "https://aphid.fireside.fm/d/1437767933/f0f20376-8faf-4940-b920-84af6c734e2d/0f4a2ab9-d3a0-41ad-8db1-6c03c851bd70.mp3",
      "thumbnail": "https://media24.fireside.fm/file/fireside-images-2024/podcasts/images/f/f0f20376-8faf-4940-b920-84af6c734e2d/cover.jpg?v=6",
      "duration": 3561,
      "published": "2026-03-31T17:00:00-07:00",
      "hasTranscript": false,
      "transcriptPreview": "“龙虾热”正在退潮，但它带来的创新冲击还在持续——当它与行业know-how相结合，正在迸发出新的能量。 阿里国际站有着26年的B2B数据和经验积累，今年初，OpenClaw、Cowork这些工作范式被验证，让他们看到了打通B2B闭环的智能体，终于到了可以落地的临界点。 于是春节之后，“外贸版龙虾”Accio Work来了，海外用户只需要和这个Agent对话，它就能自主跑完从市场分析、选品设计、供"
    },
    {
      "id": "pod_guigu101_pod_d97446f1_d6e3_4894_89d1_dca0a362b10b",
      "source": "硅谷101",
      "sourceId": "guigu101_pod",
      "sourceAvatar": "https://media24.fireside.fm/file/fireside-images-2024/podcasts/images/f/f0f20376-8faf-4940-b920-84af6c734e2d/cover.jpg?v=6",
      "platform": "podcast",
      "domains": [
        "AI",
        "Business",
        "Global"
      ],
      "title": "E230｜1万亿收入预期背后：英伟达的巅峰与软肋",
      "url": "https://aphid.fireside.fm/d/1437767933/f0f20376-8faf-4940-b920-84af6c734e2d/d97446f1-d6e3-4894-89d1-dca0a362b10b.mp3",
      "thumbnail": "https://media24.fireside.fm/file/fireside-images-2024/podcasts/images/f/f0f20376-8faf-4940-b920-84af6c734e2d/cover.jpg?v=6",
      "duration": 3981,
      "published": "2026-03-25T17:00:00-07:00",
      "hasTranscript": false,
      "transcriptPreview": "本期播客是硅谷101在GTC 2026大会期间的线下特别录制，我们从老黄在Keynote上抛出的那几个大数字开始聊起： 1万亿——这是黄仁勋预期到2027年底，Blackwell和Vera Rubin两个平台带来的订单收入。 7块——这是大会一次性发布的Vera Rubin新芯片数量。 10倍、35倍——这是Vera Rubin NVL72 AI机架系统，相比Blackwell，它的推理效率提升了"
